data.description: Welcome to 3108 Cascadia, where an exceptional single-family home awaits you offering a perfect blend of comfort and style. With its desirable features and prime location, this home is truly a gem. With 5 beds and 3 full baths, this home has plenty of space to accommodate everyone's needs. Boasting 3606 sq ft, this home provides ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Custom flooring throughout adds a touch of elegance to the interior. You'll find two separate living spaces, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying family time. On those chilly nights, cozy up by the fireplace in the master bedroom or living room for ultimate relaxation. One of the many highlights of this property is its serene backyard with no rear neighbors that backs to Canyon Hill Canal providing tranquility in your own private oasis. Parking will never be an issue with the 3-car garage along with RV parking that ensures plenty of space for your vehicles. This home does not disappoint! Call today to schedule your showing!
